<solution>
<p><ul><li>4.3994901955143</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={1450}{e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{3345}={1450}{e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{3345}}{{1450}}={e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{3345}}{{1450}}\right)}}}={0.19}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{3345}}{{1450}}\right)}}}}{{0.19}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={4.3994901955143}</m></p>
</solution>
